{"tid":279464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥每一年去EA美國遊戲展 都著同一件衫","createTime":"2017-06-11T10:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T02:57:58.000Z","uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a13b9f753fbf615bbd05af50c61cfc735a71176","tid":279464,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/11/180150_3b8a878541ea45817d91cb170b35f1c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F11%2F180150_3b8a878541ea45817d91cb170b35f1c5.jpg&h=1e821517&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a1ecc3038d2856eb574f92d07536608534dabb5","tid":279464,"uid":50769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"找到一件適合自己的衫，就好比遇到命中注定的人，認定了就不要放手，一野轟落去。<br />\n<br />\n達叔這件花花袖裇衫，就盡顯他專一又持久的一面。雖然佬編不太喜歡花巧、太有「design」的裇衫，但在達叔秀麗的長髮、高俏的身型、大智若愚的氣質加持下，卻是無可否認的相襯。<br />\n<br />\n對於這種老夫子式的買衫方法，佬訊予以絕對肯定。人生有太多選擇，將部份生活難題潛移默化為習慣，也不失為一個防止卡關的好方法。<br />\n<br />\n不過，業務繁忙如Obama也至少有一灰一藍兩套西裝，蔡思達你至少都換換條白褲，我地完啦好嘛？<br />\n<br />\nSource：King Jer 娛樂台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/loshunmag/posts/1568756606509093:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Floshunmag%2Fposts%2F1568756606509093%3A0&d=UIjRYLS3sldkIsoi36SRFzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a21e7fb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/loshunmag/posts/1568756606509093:0</a>"},{"pid":"c46346ba702a706ea451b8f63f1ea837165adf95","tid":279464,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"無高過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18626199db3b89a7161ade0afac46c99bdfb9ce9","tid":279464,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aeddc917a39cd0c6e6977b4cb1f44a8deda43de","tid":